{{root|en|ine-pro|*gʷṓws}}
From {{bor|en|pt|-}} or {{bor|en|es|búfalo||buffalo}}, from {{der|en|LL.|būfalus}}, from {{der|en|la|būbalus}}, from {{der|en|grc|βούβαλος||antelope, wild ox}}.

