===Noun===
{{en-noun|buffaloes|s|buffalo}}

# {{senseid|en|old world mammal}} Any of the Old World mammals of the family [[Bovidae]], such as the [[Cape buffalo]], {{taxlink|Syncerus caffer|species}}, or the [[water buffalo]] ''[[Bubalus bubalis]]''.
#: {{syn|en|buffle<q:obsolete>}}
#* {{RQ:Haggard She|passage="It must be a very wild stretch of country, and full of big game. I have always wanted to kill a '''buffalo''' before I die."}}
# {{senseid|en|bison}} A related North American animal, the [[American bison]], ''[[Bison bison]]''.
# {{ellipsis of|en|buffalo robe}}
# The [[buffalo fish]] (''[[Ictiobus]]'' spp.).
# {{lb|en|US|_|slang}} A [[nickel]].

